&lt;ol&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#%E9%A1%8C%E7%9B%AE%E6%95%98%E8%BF%B0&#34;&gt;crossword &lt;em&gt;n. 縱橫填字遊戲&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;A game in which you write words that are the answers to questions in a pattern of black and white squares.&lt;br&gt;
&lt;strong&gt;ex.&lt;/strong&gt; &lt;em&gt;I do the Times crossword every morning.&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
